name: Bright and airy room
description: We have a quiet and sunny room with a good view in our 3 bedroom flat. In a welcoming atmosphere, our clean and respectful flatshare is located in a leafy neighbourhood with all facilities: shops, library, cafés and bars, a swimming pools, gyms, and fantastic parks. Well connected by metro and bus with the centre: 15 minutes. For walks, we are also a 20 min stroll away from the riverside. I am living in a nice flat near the centre of Madrid (15 minutes by bus). We are relaxed, clean, and independent. The flat is located in a leafy neighbourhood with plenty of facilities: little shops, supermarkets, public library, swimming pools (covered and summer ones), tennis courts and free parking outside the flat. It is well connected by public transport (various bus and metro lines). The room is sunny and well presented. There are two bathrooms, one of which you would share with a guest. It has triple glazing and we provide fresh bedlinen and towels, so that packing is lighter for our guests. We
neighborhood_overview: We live in a leafy neighbourhood with plenty of green areas and recreational opportunities such as the library, gyms, swimming pools (covered and summer ones), and the tennis courts. Parking is free outside and it is relatively easy to park near the flat.
notes: We are a 15 min bus ride away from the Casa de Campo forest, as well as the zoo and the theme park there. We are also a 20 min stroll to the riverside, and just 5 minutes away from a fantastic park: great for runs and walks. On the other hand, it is not a comfortable accommodation for pets.
transit: The flat is near the centre of Madrid (15 minutes by bus). We are well connect by public transport: several buses (31 and 138 and more), metro line L6 and Cercanías trains. If you are bringing your car, parking is free outside. There is a bycicle lane too.
access: There is fibre optic internet connection for you to use. We share the living room and the bathroom is normally shared with one other person only, as there are actually two bathrooms in the flat. Please make sure you you take care to keep it nice and clean, just as we do. Guests can use the kitchen when staying for more than 3 nights.
interaction: If I am at home and see each other around here, it will be a pleasure to have interesting talks. If you need to ask or let me know about anything, feel free to knock on my bedroom door.
house_rules: Many thanks for not smoking at home.

name: Select the Madrid more "cool".
description: Select the Madrid more "cool" : 70 m, 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, living room with stereo and TV kitchenette equipped with microwave and Hob. Traditional building restored in the Centre, 10 minutes walk from the Puerta del Sol, next to Gran Vía and many restaurants, theatres, museums and all the cultural offer of the capital. Public transport: Metro Bank of Spain/Chueca/Gran Vía, nearby train, several bus lines,... El Madrid mas "cool" : Piso con unos 70 m, 2 dormitorios, 1 baño completo, salón comedor con equipo de música y TV. Cocina americana equipada con vitroceramica y microondas.  El apartamento se encuentra dentro de un edifio tradicional rehabilitado, en pleno centro, a 10 minutos andando de la Puerta del Sol, junto a Gran Vía y y al recién reformado Mercado de San Antón, donde podrás degustar todo tipo de tapas o tomar una copa en su terraza en la última planta. Es un barrio animado con múltiples restaurantes y bares de copas. A pocos pasos puedes encontrar las tiendas mas vanguar
neighborhood_overview: Cosmopolita, lleno de locales de moda, restaurantes y tiendas vanguardistas. Un barrio divertido, especialmente en fines de semana.
notes: Al estar en el distrito Centro (Barrio de Justicia), es equidistante a las distintas áreas de la ciudad. Es de especial mención la cercanía al 'Parque del Buen Retiro', principal parque de la ciudad, mandado construir por Felipe IV para su disfrute en el siglo XVII.
transit: La situación del apartamento hace accesibles a pie lamayor parte de puntos de interés, sin embargo rodeando al apartamento se encuentran tres estaciones distintas de Metro (Gran Vía -línea 1-, Banco de España -línea 2- y Chueca -línea 5-. También cercan están las estaciones 'Recoletos' y 'Sol' de tren Cercanías Renfe, así como varías líneas de autobús incluyendo Aeropuerto Exprés 24h.
access: La disponibilidad de acceso al apartamento es total para el huésped.
interaction: El precio marcado es por el alojamiento completo. Recibimos personalmente a los huéspedes para proporcionarles la información que puedan necesitar. A pesar del horario previsto para 'check-in' y check-out, intentamos la mayor flexibilidad para comodidad del viajero.
house_rules: Esperamos que los huéspedes traten la casa como si fuera suya. La disfruten y la respeten.
